555
00:28:59,630 --> 00:29:01,670
So, I've given them all

556
00:29:01,700 --> 00:29:02,700
a task,

557
00:29:03,880 --> 00:29:06,380
which is to gather information about Lei Hong.

558
00:29:06,380 --> 00:29:07,530
Brilliant.

559
00:29:07,560 --> 00:29:09,770
Now, we need to

560
00:29:10,040 --> 00:29:11,320
cast this wide net.

561
00:29:12,190 --> 00:29:12,850
Do you think

562
00:29:12,870 --> 00:29:14,870
we should get involved in Lord Xiu's

563
00:29:15,440 --> 00:29:17,170
Wealth Building Hall business

564
00:29:17,750 --> 00:29:19,080
