565
00:29:20,920 --> 00:29:23,110
I'll sell novels and magazines, of course.

566
00:29:23,110 --> 00:29:25,560
If they don't sell, at least we can read them ourselves.

567
00:29:25,560 --> 00:29:26,620
It won't be wasted.

568
00:29:28,050 --> 00:29:30,680
Then I'll open a military bookstore

569
00:29:31,270 --> 00:29:34,030
