570
00:29:36,530 --> 00:29:38,410
Educate culture? So funny.

571
00:29:41,770 --> 00:29:42,550
What about you?

572
00:29:42,550 --> 00:29:45,150
What's the easiest money to make in this world?

573
00:29:45,600 --> 00:29:47,660
Women's money is the easiest to make.

574
00:29:48,190 --> 00:29:50,630
You can make a lot of money just by using

575
00:29:51,300 --> 00:29:53,160
the flowers and grasses outside.

576
00:29:54,540 --> 00:29:56,270
Where's Zichuan Xiu? Come out!

577
00:29:56,620 --> 00:29:57,180
Here.

578
00:29:58,180 --> 00:30:00,510
What's this Wealth Building Hall? We quit.

579
00:30:00,510 --> 00:30:01,630
Yes, we quit.

580
00:30:02,120 --> 00:30:03,670
Gentlemen, calm down.

581
00:30:03,880 --> 00:30:05,270
How can you refuse such an opportunity

582
00:30:05,270 --> 00:30:06,290
to become wealthy?

583
00:30:06,290 --> 00:30:07,420
What good business?

584
