589
00:30:14,850 --> 00:30:17,510
Are you relying on these incompetent soldiers?

590
00:30:20,990 --> 00:30:21,650
The Xiu Battalion

591
00:30:21,650 --> 00:30:23,450
is not a group of ragtag soldiers

592
00:30:23,770 --> 00:30:26,270
They have undergone professional military training.

593
00:30:26,270 --> 00:30:27,320
Their martial arts...

594
00:30:27,320 --> 00:30:28,450
Ho! Ho! Ha!

595
00:30:29,030 --> 00:30:31,230
I've heard this slogan a hundred times.

596
00:30:31,390 --> 00:30:32,960
No matter how loudly you chant your slogans,

597
00:30:32,960 --> 00:30:35,920
what's the use of just these few soldiers?

598
00:30:36,270 --> 00:30:37,030
You...

599
00:30:40,170 --> 00:30:41,410
What you see now

600
00:30:41,650 --> 00:30:43,530
is only a small part of our forces.

601
00:30:43,680 --> 00:30:44,340
Put it down.

602
00:30:45,110 --> 00:30:47,150
Actually, our forces

603
00:30:47,170 --> 00:30:48,980
are distributed throughout Yuanzhou,

604
00:30:48,980 --> 00:30:51,500
and even infiltrated into the territory of the North Clan.

605
00:30:51,500 --> 00:30:53,060
You don't need to worry about the issue of military strength.

606
00:30:53,060 --> 00:30:55,170
We didn't see the army with our own eyes.

607
00:30:55,170 --> 00:30:56,710
So we still find it difficult to believe in your promise.

608
00:30:56,710 --> 00:30:58,640
Are you worried that our Zichuan family's army

609
00:30:58,640 --> 00:30:59,840
is not strong enough?

610
00:30:59,970 --> 00:31:00,960
Princess Ning.

611
00:31:03,880 --> 00:31:05,160
I've been to the Imperial Capital.

612
00:31:05,160 --> 00:31:07,290
This is really Princess Zichuan Ning.

613
00:31:07,800 --> 00:31:08,800
Your Highness,

614
00:31:09,560 --> 00:31:11,690
I can guarantee on behalf of our family

615
00:31:11,690 --> 00:31:13,690
that all your deals in Yuanzhou

616
00:31:13,720 --> 00:31:15,780
will always be protected by the army.

617
00:31:15,930 --> 00:31:17,270
Does that reassure all of you?

618
00:31:17,270 --> 00:31:18,190
Yes.

619
00:31:18,190 --> 00:31:19,310
Yes.

620
00:31:27,180 --> 00:31:28,370
Then please

621
00:31:28,400 --> 00:31:30,680
accompany us to see our army camp.

622
00:31:32,820 --> 00:31:33,790
Please.

623
00:31:33,990 --> 00:31:35,430
Okay, goodbye.

624
00:31:35,460 --> 00:31:36,020
Goodbye.

625
00:31:39,940 --> 00:31:40,700
Let's go.

626
00:31:50,080 --> 00:31:52,280
Ning, thank you for helping me out.

627
00:31:53,310 --> 00:31:54,970
I didn't expect you to be so capable.

628
00:31:54,970 --> 00:31:55,440
You...

629
00:31:55,470 --> 00:31:57,440
You didn't expect that I would help you

630
00:31:57,440 --> 00:31:59,300
establish yourself in Yuanzhou?

631
00:32:06,380 --> 00:32:07,690
Let's split up

632
00:32:08,150 --> 00:32:09,990
and go to different tribal cities

633
00:32:09,990 --> 00:32:13,320
to persuade the merchants to join our Wealth Building Hall.

634
00:32:22,430 --> 00:32:24,910
You must have been out for a long time.

635
00:32:25,750 --> 00:32:27,050
Do you miss

636
00:32:27,190 --> 00:32:29,830
the food and wine in your hometown?

637
00:32:30,730 --> 00:32:33,010
Do you feel uncomfortable

638
00:32:33,070 --> 00:32:34,310
and frustrated living here?

639
00:32:34,310 --> 00:32:37,070
Welcome to the Xiu Battalion's Wealth Building Hall.

640
00:32:37,070 --> 00:32:38,150
Welcome.

641
00:32:39,810 --> 00:32:40,980
I'll take the wine.

642
00:32:41,860 --> 00:32:43,300
Okay, pay me.

643
00:32:44,270 --> 00:32:45,200
I want this one.

644
00:32:45,320 --> 00:32:45,790
What's the rush?

645
00:32:45,790 --> 00:32:46,310
OK.

646
00:32:46,310 --> 00:32:46,780
We have plenty.

647
00:32:46,780 --> 00:32:48,850
Everyone, let me introduce

648
00:32:48,860 --> 00:32:51,860
the next product, Snake Race's Secret Recipe Sausage.

649
00:32:51,860 --> 00:32:54,670
Three, two, one. Put it up.

650
00:32:54,730 --> 00:32:56,060
I want it.

651
00:32:56,080 --> 00:32:56,620
Don't grab.

652
00:32:56,620 --> 00:32:57,540
I want it too.

653
00:32:57,950 --> 00:32:59,550
We have all kinds of delicious food and wine.

654
00:32:59,550 --> 00:33:00,880
If you want anything else,

655
00:33:00,880 --> 00:33:01,950
we can pre-sell it.

656
00:33:02,070 --> 00:33:03,030
Tell Captain Luo Jie

657
00:33:03,030 --> 00:33:04,590
what you want,

658
00:33:04,730 --> 00:33:06,100
and he will record it all.

659
00:33:06,100 --> 00:33:06,710
Also,

660
00:33:07,630 --> 00:33:09,950
in a couple of days, it will be payday,

661
00:33:10,150 --> 00:33:12,760
and I will hold a gathering here.

662
00:33:12,790 --> 00:33:16,030
Remember to bring your friends along,

663
00:33:16,050 --> 00:33:19,450
and there will be discounts for you.

664
00:33:19,670 --> 00:33:20,510
Okay.

665
00:33:34,470 --> 00:33:34,920
Here.

666
00:33:44,780 --> 00:33:45,810
This dish

667
00:33:47,230 --> 00:33:51,340
is my beloved wife Shuzhen's specialty.

668
00:33:52,120 --> 00:33:53,800
She knew I liked it.

669
00:33:55,110 --> 00:33:56,910
She often cooked it for me.

670
00:34:00,190 --> 00:34:01,030
Now,

671
00:34:03,830 --> 00:34:05,350
my beloved wife is gone.

672
00:34:06,740 --> 00:34:07,310
I...

673
00:34:09,110 --> 00:34:11,540
I can't taste her cooking anymore.

674
00:34:12,340 --> 00:34:16,219
I know you are an upright official.

675
00:34:16,980 --> 00:34:22,300
The graveyard you bought for your deceased wife was too simple.

676
00:34:22,820 --> 00:34:26,260
The cemetery I bought

677
00:34:35,010 --> 00:34:39,550
for your late wife is of noble standard.

678
00:35:14,300 --> 00:35:18,180
My Lord, I'm ashamed.

679
00:35:19,620 --> 00:35:22,220
Corruption among the bureaucrats of Yuanzhou

680
00:35:22,750 --> 00:35:24,650
is a deep-rooted problem.

681
00:35:26,440 --> 00:35:29,290
It will eventually require strong measures.

682
00:35:32,070 --> 00:35:32,790
However,

683
00:35:35,260 --> 00:35:42,410
Gu Lan is my last remaining relative.

684
00:35:58,340 --> 00:36:01,900
But precisely because he is my relative,

685
00:36:02,280 --> 00:36:04,000
he must die.

686
00:36:06,120 --> 00:36:08,040
Only then can it be made clear

687
00:36:09,780 --> 00:36:13,140
that our family is determined to cleanse our ranks.

688
00:36:39,390 --> 00:36:40,500
Be a true man.

689
00:36:44,470 --> 00:36:46,790
Eat. This is your last meal.

690
00:37:51,670 --> 00:37:53,960
Brother-in-law.

691
00:37:54,630 --> 00:37:55,640
I will resign from my office.

692
00:37:55,640 --> 00:37:56,910
I will live in seclusion.

693
00:37:56,910 --> 00:37:58,690
I will no longer cause trouble for you.

694
00:37:58,690 --> 00:37:59,690
Brother-in-law.

695
00:37:59,790 --> 00:38:01,500
For the sake of my sister,

696
00:38:02,500 --> 00:38:04,400
please spare my life.

697
00:38:07,620 --> 00:38:10,560
Luo Minghai, you betrayed my sister.

698
00:38:10,580 --> 00:38:12,050
You betrayed my family.

699
00:38:12,990 --> 00:38:14,800
You didn't even save your own people.

700
00:38:14,800 --> 00:38:16,320
You have no conscience.

701
00:38:16,840 --> 00:38:19,010
My sister and I will never...

702
00:38:32,980 --> 00:38:33,730
Di Lin.

703
00:38:39,190 --> 00:38:41,150
Are you satisfied now?

704
00:38:42,040 --> 00:38:44,070
On the night when the people of Yuanzhou

705
00:38:44,070 --> 00:38:45,730
bled in the Imperial Capital,

706
00:38:49,340 --> 00:38:51,130
my entire family,

707
00:38:53,900 --> 00:38:55,890
including the present Gu Lan,

708
00:38:58,390 --> 00:39:03,040
your hands are probably stained with blood that can never be washed away.

709
00:39:08,880 --> 00:39:10,790
So, please, in the future, when the Ministry of War and the Ministry of Government Supervision

710
00:39:10,790 --> 00:39:12,590
inspect local finances,

711
00:39:12,610 --> 00:39:13,540
be more careful.

712
00:39:15,480 --> 00:39:16,810
Don't be like this time,

713
00:39:17,000 --> 00:39:18,430
which led to the Lord Chieftain ordering punishment

714
00:39:18,430 --> 00:39:20,030
and left me covered in blood.

715
00:39:32,400 --> 00:39:33,070
Kill!

716
00:40:29,270 --> 00:40:30,290
You're back.

717
00:40:36,500 --> 00:40:37,270
Is it nice?

718
00:40:38,750 --> 00:40:39,590
Yes.

719
00:40:44,780 --> 00:40:47,180
I've been feeling like he's moving lately.

720
00:40:50,350 --> 00:40:51,190
What's wrong?

721
00:40:51,720 --> 00:40:53,180
I'm going to wash my hands.

722
00:40:56,830 --> 00:40:58,630
Your hands are probably stained

723
00:40:58,950 --> 00:41:01,270
with blood that can never be washed away.

724
00:41:02,430 --> 00:41:04,350
I hope that one day

725
00:41:05,230 --> 00:41:07,860
you will experience the same pain.

726
00:41:09,520 --> 00:41:11,380
Retribution will not be delayed.

727
00:41:13,650 --> 00:41:15,450
Ever since I felt it move,

728
00:41:16,150 --> 00:41:17,350
I've been wondering

729
00:41:18,230 --> 00:41:22,030
if this child will be like you or like me.

730
00:41:29,160 --> 00:41:31,720
He can't be like me, my eyes are too small.

731
00:41:32,110 --> 00:41:33,240
He has to be like you.

732
00:41:34,510 --> 00:41:36,270
I'd rather he be like you.

733
00:41:37,190 --> 00:41:39,990
I only know how to cook, I don't know anything else.

734
00:41:40,110 --> 00:41:41,040
That's not true.

735
00:41:41,680 --> 00:41:44,230
In my eyes, being able to cook and take care of the family

736
00:41:44,230 --> 00:41:45,090
is a real skill.

737
00:41:46,790 --> 00:41:47,810
Everyone is pursuing

738
00:41:47,810 --> 00:41:49,730
fame and fortune.

739
00:41:50,090 --> 00:41:51,090
But in my opinion,

740
00:41:51,870 --> 00:41:53,670
those are just fleeting dreams.

741
00:41:55,390 --> 00:41:57,050
Who knows when they'll wake up

742
00:41:57,710 --> 00:41:59,510
and nothing will exist anymore?

743
00:42:03,480 --> 00:42:05,920
Why are you suddenly so emotional today?

744
00:42:06,290 --> 00:42:07,550
Did something happen?

745
00:42:08,510 --> 00:42:10,830
Nothing. I want to tell you

746
00:42:11,650 --> 00:42:14,270
that in this world, only love and hatred are real.

747
00:42:14,270 --> 00:42:16,760
Being able to give warmth and beauty to another person

748
00:42:16,760 --> 00:42:18,020
is the greatest skill.

749
00:42:19,340 --> 00:42:22,010
And you gave me a home.

750
00:42:23,030 --> 00:42:24,100
So in my eyes,

751
00:42:24,120 --> 00:42:26,980
you're better than all the officials and generals.

752
00:42:28,050 --> 00:42:28,630
Besides,

753
00:42:30,640 --> 00:42:34,770
no one is more precious to me than you.

754
00:42:48,670 --> 00:42:50,930
If it were someone else,

755
00:42:51,670 --> 00:42:53,530
he would have been overcautious.

756
00:42:54,270 --> 00:42:56,860
Only Big Brother can be so decisive.

757
00:42:57,860 --> 00:42:59,920
Even if he makes enemies everywhere,

758
00:43:00,720 --> 00:43:02,350
and not understood by the world...
